---
<section class="hero-split" id="top">
  <div class="container hero-split-inner">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <span class="eyebrow">FTP · SFTP · FTPS</span>
      <h1>FileZilla 下载</h1>
      <p class="hero-lead">面向网站部署、服务器运维与文件同步场景，整理 FileZilla 在 Windows、macOS、Linux 上的安装配置、站点管理、FTP 与 SFTP 传输方法。</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/dows.html">进入下载中心</a>
        <a class="btn btn-outline" href="#latest">查看文章更新</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-visual">
      <img src="https://tse-mm.bing.com/th?q=FileZilla%20FTP%20client%20interface" alt="FileZilla FTP 客户端主界面展示" loading="eager" width="480" height="320">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="stats-bar" id="overview">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="stats-row">
      <div class="stat-item"><strong>FTP</strong><span>标准文件传输协议</span></div>
      <div class="stat-item"><strong>SFTP</strong><span>SSH 加密通道传输</span></div>
      <div class="stat-item"><strong>FTPS</strong><span>SSL/TLS 安全连接</span></div>
      <div class="stat-item"><strong>跨平台</strong><span>Windows / macOS / Linux</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="platforms">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="section-head">
      <h2>FileZilla 客户端入口</h2>
    </header>
    <div class="platform-grid">
      <article class="platform-card">
        <a href="/blog/filezilla-windows-install-guide/">
          <img src="https://tse-mm.bing.com/th?q=FileZilla%20Windows%20FTP%20client" alt="FileZilla Windows 版 FTP 客户端界面" loading="lazy">
        </a>
        <div class="platform-body">
          <h3>Windows 版</h3>
          <p>适合桌面开发、网站部署与远程文件管理，覆盖安装、站点配置与首次 FTP 连接。</p>
          <a class="card-link" href="/blog/filezilla-windows-install-guide/">查看安装步骤</a>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="platform-card">
        <a href="/blog/filezilla-macos-install-steps/">
          <img src="https://tse-mm.bing.com/th?q=FileZilla%20macOS%20SFTP" alt="FileZilla macOS 版 SFTP 传输界面" loading="lazy">
        </a>
        <div class="platform-body">
          <h3>macOS 版</h3>
          <p>整理芯片兼容、权限确认与拖拽传输，便于本地与云端服务器文件同步。</p>
          <a class="card-link" href="/blog/filezilla-macos-install-steps/">查看安装步骤</a>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="platform-card">
        <a href="/blog/filezilla-linux-sftp-setup/">
          <img src="https://tse-mm.bing.com/th?q=FileZilla%20Linux%20FTP%20setup" alt="FileZilla Linux 环境 FTP 配置" loading="lazy">
        </a>
        <div class="platform-body">
          <h3>Linux 环境</h3>
          <p>连接本地与远程 Linux 主机的 FTP 与 SFTP 基础设置与命令行配合使用。</p>
          <a class="card-link" href="/blog/filezilla-linux-sftp-setup/">阅读详情</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="features">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="section-head">
      <h2>FileZilla 常用能力</h2>
    </header>
    <div class="zigzag">
      {% set items = [
        ["站点管理器", "保存多组服务器连接信息，按项目或环境快速切换。"],
        ["双栏文件浏览", "本地与远程目录并排显示，拖拽即可完成上传下载。"],
        ["传输队列", "批量文件按队列顺序传输，支持暂停与恢复。"],
        ["SFTP 加密", "通过 SSH 通道安全传输敏感文件与配置文件。"],
        ["书签功能", "为常用远程目录创建书签，减少重复导航。"],
        ["被动模式", "配合防火墙与 NAT 环境完成稳定连接。"],
        ["目录比较", "对比本地与远程文件差异，便于增量同步。"],
        ["日志面板", "实时查看连接与传输日志，快速定位问题。"]
      ] %}
      {% for item in items %}
        <article class="zigzag-row">
          <div class="zigzag-num">{{ loop.index }}</div>
          <div class="zigzag-body">
            <h3>{{ item[0] }}</h3>
            <p>{{ item[1] }}</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="latest">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="section-head">
      <h2>FileZilla 文章更新</h2>
    </header>
    <div class="mosaic">
      {% for post in collections.posts | sortByDateDesc %}
        {% if loop.index <= 12 %}
          <article class="mosaic-card">
            {% if post.data.heroImage %}
              <a href="{{ post.url }}">
                <img src="{{ post.data.heroImage }}" alt="{{ post.data.heroAlt or post.data.title }}" loading="lazy">
              </a>
            {% endif %}
            <div class="mosaic-body">
              <time class="mosaic-date" datetime="{{ post.date | readableDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
              <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
              <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="catalog-band" id="catalog">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="section-head">
      <h2>内容目录</h2>
    </header>
    <nav class="pill-scroll" aria-label="内容目录">
      {% for cat in collections.publicCategories %}
        <a href="/categories/{{ cat | categorySlug }}/">{{ cat }}</a>
      {% endfor %}
      <a href="/tags/">Tags 聚合</a>
      <a href="/blog/">全部文章</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</section>
